# SEO Check

Audit search engine optimization for OakStone Properties.

## Quick Audit

```bash
npm run build
# Then check dist/ for:
# - sitemap.xml
# - robots.txt
# - Proper meta tags in HTML files
```

## Full SEO Workflow

### 1. Meta Tags Validation

#### Homepage (`src/pages/index.astro`)
```html
<title>OakStone Properties | Rental Homes in [City]</title>
<meta name="description" content="Browse available rental properties..." />
<meta property="og:title" content="OakStone Properties" />
<meta property="og:description" content="..." />
<meta property="og:image" content="/og-image.jpg" />
<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
<link rel="canonical" href="https://domain.com/" />
```

#### Property Pages (`src/pages/properties/[slug].astro`)
```html
<title>{property.title} | OakStone Properties</title>
<meta name="description" content="{beds}BR/{baths}BA in {neighborhood}. ${rent}/mo..." />
<meta property="og:title" content="{property.title}" />
<meta property="og:description" content="..." />
<meta property="og:image" content="{first photo}" />
<meta property="og:type" content="article" />
```

### 2. Schema.org Markup

#### RentalListing Schema (for property pages)

```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "RentalListing",
  "name": "Property Title",
  "description": "Property description",
  "address": {
    "@type": "PostalAddress",
    "addressLocality": "City",
    "addressRegion": "ST",
    "addressCountry": "US"
  },
  "numberOfRooms": 3,
  "numberOfBedrooms": 2,
  "numberOfBathroomsTotal": 1,
  "floorSize": {
    "@type": "QuantitativeValue",
    "value": 950,
    "unitCode": "FTK"
  },
  "price": {
    "@type": "MonetaryAmount",
    "currency": "USD",
    "value": 1500
  },
  "image": ["photo1.jpg", "photo2.jpg"],
  "url": "https://domain.com/properties/slug"
}
```

Add to property layout:
```astro
<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schemaData)} />
```

#### LocalBusiness Schema (for About page)

