### 3. Technical SEO

#### robots.txt (`public/robots.txt`)
```
User-agent: *
Allow: /

Sitemap: https://domain.com/sitemap.xml
```

#### Sitemap Configuration

In `astro.config.mjs`:
```javascript
import sitemap from '@astrojs/sitemap';

export default defineConfig({
  site: 'https://domain.com',
  integrations: [sitemap()],
});
```

Verify sitemap includes:
- [ ] Homepage
- [ ] All property pages
- [ ] About, Contact, FAQ pages
- [ ] Property listing page

### 4. Image SEO

Every image needs:
- [ ] Descriptive filename (`living-room.webp` not `IMG_1234.webp`)
- [ ] Alt text describing the content
- [ ] Proper dimensions (not oversized)
- [ ] Modern format (WebP preferred)

```astro
<img
  src={photo}
  alt={`Living room of ${property.title}`}
  width="800"
  height="600"
  loading="lazy"
/>
```

### 5. URL Structure

Good:
- `/properties/cozy-2br-downtown`
- `/properties/` (listing page)
- `/about`
- `/contact`

Bad:
- `/properties/123` (numeric IDs)
- `/p/abc` (short/cryptic)
- `/properties.html` (file extensions)

### 6. Performance (Core Web Vitals)

| Metric | Target | Tool |
|--------|--------|------|
| LCP | <2.5s | Lighthouse |
| FID | <100ms | Lighthouse |
| CLS | <0.1 | Lighthouse |

Impact on SEO:
- Google uses Core Web Vitals as ranking factors
- Slow sites get lower rankings

### 7. Mobile-First

- [ ] Viewport meta tag present
- [ ] Touch targets >= 48px
- [ ] Text readable without zoom
- [ ] No horizontal scrolling
- [ ] Mobile-friendly test passes

```html
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
```

### 8. Local SEO (Important for Rentals)

- [ ] Google Business Profile (owner sets up)
- [ ] Consistent NAP (Name, Address, Phone) across site
- [ ] City/neighborhood mentioned in content
- [ ] Local schema markup

